		{"id":"v2r2-06-prompt","type":"text","text":"**NB2 Prompt:** `06-category-inventory.txt`\n\nCreate a static ad for Lifeforce's comprehensive health testing membership. 1080x1920, 9:16 vertical.\n\nCOMPOSITION:\nOne continuous image filling the entire frame. The background is a full-bleed warm cellular organic texture. Close-up microscopic photography of golden-amber organic cells or molecular structures, softly blurred and warmly lit. Rounded, translucent, overlapping cells in warm amber, golden brown, and honey tones. Lifeforce's signature background. Soft-edged, gently luminous, slightl...","x":830,"y":21160,"width":400,"height":400},
		{"id":"v2r2-07-label","type":"text","text":"**Concept 7: Ad #12 — Us vs Them: Data Without a Doctor (Us vs Them Style A)**","x":-140,"y":21640,"width":960,"height":30},
		{"id":"v2r2-07-1","type":"file","file":"Lifeforce/00 Assets/Statics/ref-07-data-without-doctor/variant-1.png","x":-140,"y":21680,"width":223,"height":400},
