		{"id":"v2r2-07-4","type":"file","file":"Lifeforce/00 Assets/Statics/ref-07-data-without-doctor/variant-4.png","x":580,"y":21680,"width":223,"height":400},
		{"id":"v2r2-07-prompt","type":"text","text":"**NB2 Prompt:** `07-data-without-doctor.txt`\n\nCreate a static ad for Lifeforce's comprehensive health testing membership. 1080x1920, 9:16 vertical.\n\nCOMPOSITION:\nThe frame is divided into two columns by a clean vertical line at x=490. The left column is visually muted and suppressed. The right column is warm and vibrant. The split creates two different worlds.\n\nLEFT COLUMN — \"OTHER HEALTH PLATFORMS\" (x=0 to x=480):\nBackground: desaturated, cool-grey toned. A subtle texture of flat, lifeless grey — think a dull concrete or sterile medical of...","x":830,"y":21680,"width":400,"height":400},
		{"id":"v2r2-08-label","type":"text","text":"**Concept 8: Ad #4 — Stress/Low T IG Stories Q&A**","x":-140,"y":22160,"width":960,"height":30},
		{"id":"v2r2-08-2","type":"file","file":"Lifeforce/00 Assets/Statics/ref-08-stress-igstory/variant-2.png","x":100,"y":22200,"width":223,"height":400},
		{"id":"v2r2-08-3","type":"file","file":"Lifeforce/00 Assets/Statics/ref-08-stress-igstory/variant-3.png","x":340,"y":22200,"width":223,"height":400},
		{"id":"v2r2-08-4","type":"file","file":"Lifeforce/00 Assets/Statics/ref-08-stress-igstory/variant-4.png","x":580,"y":22200,"width":223,"height":400},
		{"id":"v2r2-08-prompt","type":"text","text":"**NB2 Prompt:** `08-stress-lowt-igstory.txt`\n\nCreate a static ad mimicking a native Instagram Stories Q&A response. 1080x1920, 9:16 vertical.\n\nCRITICAL: This must look like a real Instagram Story, not a designed ad. Every UI element must match Instagram's actual Stories tools — the \"Ask me anything\" sticker, the text-with-background blocks, the font sizing and spacing. It must feel like a real person posted this, not a brand.\n\nBACKGROUND:\nFull-bleed lifestyle photograph filling the entire 1080x1920 frame. A man in his late 30s sits at a hom...","x":830,"y":22200,"width":400,"height":400},
